rdf:Description.dc:title: Icosohedral orthodromic mesh - Equirectangular projection
rdf:Description.dc:description: A mesh of great circles that intersect with 10-fold symmetry at 12 principal nodes and 6-fold symmetry at 20 minor nodes. Aligns with the edges of an icosohedron and its dual dodecahedron.
rdf:Description.dc:creator: Justin Kunimune
